  @case 'fx region (cc augment): un-automated target seats base(rest) + macro, markerless, off columns'  [harness]  @ 1440-1462
  @case 'fx region (cc augment): over authored automation the seat is authored-base + macro'  [harness]  @ 1466-1486
  @case 'fx region (cc augment): two overlapping regions sum every stream (N-stream regression guard)'  [harness]  @ 1490-1518
