  @case 'note-host augment (cc): a sounding note drives summed seats like a degenerate region'  [harness]  @ 1544-1573
  @case 'replace: a preceding on-take tail clips at the parked chord onset, not past it'  [harness]  @ 1579-1595
  @case 'replace: a derived tile is not truncated by a parked member it replaced'  [harness]  @ 1599-1615
  @case 'deleting a self-parked [trill, vibrato] host leaves no orphaned pb seats'  [harness]  @ 1621-1646
  @case 'removing the note kind from a self-parked [autopan, trill] host keeps its authored cc parked'  [harness]  @ 1652-1701

